translated: Eriksson, Nanna Matilda, dentist, Visby, born on March 4th, 1894 in Ekebyborna, Östergötland, daughter of landowner Birger Carfeson and Anna Sundström. Married to dentist Felix Eriksson in 1917. Children: Margareta, born in 1921, Bengt, born in 1923. Nanna Matilda graduated from Uppsala private high school and gymnasium in 1912, completed her dental education in 1915, and practiced in Hjo from 1915 to 1917. She has been practicing in Visby since 1917 and has been the secretary of the Gotland Dental Association since its establishment.
